'''伯特蘭·伊西多爾·特拉奧雷'''（{{lang-fr|'''Bertrand Isidore Traoré'''}}，{{bd|1995年|9月6日}}）是[[布基納法索|布基納法索]]的職業足球運動員，司職[[攻擊中場|攻擊中場]]和[[翼鋒|翼鋒]]，現效力[[英格兰足球超级联赛|英超]]球會[[阿士東維拉足球會|阿士東維拉]]。

==球會生涯==
=== 車路士 ===
2010年8月伯特蘭·特拉奧雷由[[歐賽爾足球會|歐賽爾]]轉會至[[車路士足球會|車路士]]，同時拒絕了[[曼徹斯特聯足球會|曼聯]]的邀請。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.thesun.co.uk/sol/homepage/sport/football/3091736/Burkina-Faso-prospect-Bertrand-Traore-chooses-Chelsea-over-Manchester-United.html|title=Bert chooses Blues over Utd|date=12 August 2010|accessdate=21 September 2011|publisher=''The Sun''|archive-date=2015-12-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151222135052/http://www.thesun.co.uk/sol/homepage/sport/football/3091736/Burkina-Faso-prospect-Bertrand-Traore-chooses-Chelsea-over-Manchester-United.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.tribalfootball.com/chelsea-told-they-have-signed-future-superstar-bertrand-traore-1040811|title=Chelsea told they have signed future superstar in Bertrand Traore|date=12 August 2010|accessdate=21 September 2011|publisher=Tribal Football|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120109085437/http://www.tribalfootball.com/chelsea-told-they-have-signed-future-superstar-bertrand-traore-1040811|archivedate=2012-01-09}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.goal.com/en-gb/news/2896/premier-league/2010/08/12/2067030/chelsea-beat-manchester-united-to-burkina-faso-starlet|title=Chelsea beat Manchester United to Cameroon starlet Bertrand Traore - report|date=12 August 2010|accessdate=21 September 2011|publisher=Goal.com|archive-date=2021-03-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210309211027/https://www.goal.com/en-gb/news/2896/premier-league/2010/08/12/2067030/chelsea-beat-manchester-united-to-burkina-faso-starlet|dead-url=no}}</ref>

在2011年1月，特拉奧雷仍然未正式簽約[[車路士足球會|車路士]]。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/africa/9370469.stm|title=Burkina youngster hopes to star for Chelsea|date=22 January 2011|accessdate=21 September 2011|author=Matthew Kenyon|publisher=BBC Sport}}</ref> 並在2012年1月球會證實，特拉奧雷從來未有成為[[車路士足球會|車路士]]球員，但球會的青年隊表示在賽季開始前曾參加一個為期六週的集訓。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.chelseafc.com/news-article/article/2580664 |title=Words on: African Cup of Nations |publisher=Chelsea F.C |date=18 January 2012 |accessdate=7 July 2014 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190203032128/https://www.chelseafc.com/news-article/article/2580664 |archive-date=2019-02-03 |dead-url=yes }}</ref> 在2013年7月17日，他首次亮相在賽季前的友誼賽對戰辛哈全明星隊<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.chelseafc.com/pre-season-article/article/3245123/title/final-whistle-verdict-good-start |title=FINAL WHISTLE VERDICT: GOOD START {{!}} Pre-Season {{!}} Matches {{!}} Official Site {{!}} Chelsea Football Club<!-- Bot generated title --> |access-date=2015-05-25 |archive-date=2013-07-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130719171315/http://www.chelseafc.com/pre-season-article/article/3245123/title/final-whistle-verdict-good-start |dead-url=no }}</ref>

在2013年10月31日，特拉奧雷正式簽署和[[車路士足球會|車路士]]簽約四年半。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.chelseafc.com/news-article/article/3518290/title/traore-contract-agreed |title=TRAORE CONTRACT AGREED {{!}} News Article {{!}} News {{!}} Official Site {{!}} Chelsea Football Club<!-- Bot generated title --> |access-date=2015-05-25 |archive-date=2014-02-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140216110957/http://www.chelseafc.com/news-article/article/3518290/title/traore-contract-agreed |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/24760411|title=Bertrand Traore: Chelsea to sign teenage Burkina Faso international|date=31 October 2013|accessdate=31 October 2013|publisher=BBC Sport|archive-date=2015-12-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151224053429/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/24760411|dead-url=no}}</ref>2014年1月合約正式生效。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.chelseafc.com/news-article/article/3597985/title/traore-move-completed|title=Traore Move Completed|date=1 January 2014|accessdate=1 January 2014|publisher=Chelsea F.C.|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140103070236/http://www.chelseafc.com/news-article/article/3597985/title/traore-move-completed|archivedate=2014-01-03}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/25566553|title=Bertrand Traore: Chelsea sign teenage Burkina Faso midfielder|date=1 January 2014|accessdate=2 January 2014|publisher=BBC Sport|archive-date=2015-08-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150830143415/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/25566553|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==== 租借至維迪斯 ====

2014年1月2日，特拉奧雷被租借至[[荷蘭甲組足球聯賽|荷蘭甲組足球聯賽]]中的[[維迪斯|維迪斯]]。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.vitesse.nl/vitessenl/nieuws/detail/4054|title=Bertrand Traore comes, Kakuta and Hutchinson Leave at Vitesse|date=2 January 2014|accessdate=2 January 2014|publisher=Vitesse Arnhem|archive-date=2014-06-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140616161601/http://www.vitesse.nl/vitessenl/nieuws/detail/4054|dead-url=no}}</ref>2014年1月6日，首次為球隊上陣，67分鐘入替[[盧卡斯·比亞桑|盧卡斯·比亞桑]]，2014年3月29日[[維迪斯|維迪斯]]對戰[[海倫芬體育會|海倫芬]]的賽事，半場入替[[米克·夏雲拿|米克·夏雲拿]]，67分鐘為球隊射入第2球。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://us.soccerway.com/matches/2014/03/29/netherlands/eredivisie/sbv-vitesse/sportclub-heerenveen/1478593/|title=Vitesse 2-2 Heerenveen|date=29 March 2014|publisher=soccerway.com|access-date=2015-05-25|archive-date=2016-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305092751/http://us.soccerway.com/matches/2014/03/29/netherlands/eredivisie/sbv-vitesse/sportclub-heerenveen/1478593/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2014年7月7日證實特拉奧雷將租借留在[[維迪斯|維迪斯]]整個2014-15賽季。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.chelseafc.com/news/latest-news/2014/07/traore-continues-dutch-loan.html|title=Traore continues Dutch loan|date=7 July 2014|accessdate=8 July 2014|publisher=chelseafc.com|archive-date=2020-11-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201128085316/https://www.chelseafc.com/news/latest-news/2014/07/traore-continues-dutch-loan.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

=== 阿斯頓維拉 ===

2020年12月20日，特拉奧雷以3-0擊敗對手[[西布罗姆维奇足球俱乐部|西布朗]]的比賽踢進了四年來的第一個[[英超|英超]]聯賽進球。<ref>{{Cite news|last=Oludare|first=Shina|date=20 December 2020|title=Bertrand Traore ends four-year Premier League wait with West Brom strike|work=Goal|url=https://www.goal.com/en-gb/news/bertrand-traore-ends-four-year-premier-league-wait-with-west/1cpsa300gpwz41kzy1klg31079|access-date=20 December 2020|archive-date=2021-02-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210214012055/https://www.goal.com/en-gb/news/bertrand-traore-ends-four-year-premier-league-wait-with-west/1cpsa300gpwz41kzy1klg31079|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==國際賽生涯==
特拉奧雷參加了[[2009年U17世界盃足球賽|2009年U17世界盃足球賽]]<ref>{{FIFA player|315107}}</ref>和[[2011年U17非洲錦標賽|2011年U17非洲錦標賽]]。<ref>{{cite web|title=Team sheet vs. Rwanda U17|url=http://www.cafonline.com/userfiles/file/Comp/Rwanda%20U_17_2011/Starting_List_Match1.pdf|publisher=Confederation of African Football|accessdate=21 September 2011|format=pdf|archive-date=2015-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924143319/http://www.cafonline.com/userfiles/file/Comp/Rwanda%20U_17_2011/Starting_List_Match1.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>並幫助[[布基納法索國家足球隊|布基納法索國家足球隊]]決賽中2-1擊敗[[盧旺達國家足球隊|盧旺達國家足球隊]]。<ref>{{cite web|title=Stallions trample Wasps to win U17 Cup|url=http://www.cafonline.com/competition/can-u-17_2011/news/7573-stallions-trample-wasps-to-win-u17-cup.html|publisher=Confederation of African Football|accessdate=21 September 2011|date=22 January 2011|archive-date=2018-10-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181026080616/http://www.cafonline.com/competition/can-u-17_2011/news/7573-stallions-trample-wasps-to-win-u17-cup.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2011年9月3日首次為[[布基納法索國家足球隊|布基納法索國家足球隊]]上陣，在友誼賽中對戰[[赤道畿內亞國家足球隊|赤道畿內亞國家足球隊]]。<ref>{{cite web |title=Bertrand Traoré: "Drogba et Kalou m’ont bien accueilli lorsque je suis arrivé à Chelsea" |trans_title=Bertrand Traoré: "Drogba and Kalou have welcomed me when I arrived at Chelsea" |url=http://burkina24.com/news/2011/09/17/bertrand-traore-drogba-et-kalou-m%E2%80%99ont-bien-accueilli-lorsque-je-suis-arrive-a-chelsea/ |date=17 September 2011 |accessdate=21 September 2011 |language=fr |archive-date=2013-11-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131105014437/http://burkina24.com/news/2011/09/17/bertrand-traore-drogba-et-kalou-m%E2%80%99ont-bien-accueilli-lorsque-je-suis-arrive-a-chelsea/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name = "leberry">{{cite web|title=Alain et Bertrand Traoré, le foot au coeur|trans_title=Alain and Bertrand Traoré, football at heart|url=http://www.lyonne.fr/yonne/actualite/departement/yonne-local/2011/09/07/alain-et-bertrand-traore-le-foot-au-coeur_1109874.html|publisher=lyonne.fr|language=fr|date=7 September 2011|accessdate=7 July 2014|archive-date=2020-12-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201203162235/https://www.lyonne.fr/yonne/actualite/departement/yonne-local/2011/09/07/alain-et-bertrand-traore-le-foot-au-coeur_1109874.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>首次在[[非洲國家盃|非洲國家盃]]亮相是[[2012年非洲國家盃|2012年非洲國家盃]]，分組賽中最後一場對戰[[蘇丹國家足球隊|蘇丹國家足球隊]]，在66分鐘入替[[耶美奧高|耶美奧高]]，結果比賽1-2不敵[[蘇丹國家足球隊|蘇丹國家足球隊]]，在分組賽中出局。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.soccerway.com/matches/2012/01/30/africa/africa-cup-of-nations/sudan/burkina-faso/1221462/ |title=Sudan vs. Burkina Faso |work=Soccerway |publisher=Global Sports Media |accessdate=1 February 2012 |archive-date=2019-07-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190720212518/https://www.soccerway.com/matches/2012/01/30/africa/africa-cup-of-nations/sudan/burkina-faso/1221462/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

特拉奧雷打進了他的第一個進球在2013年8月14日，客場2-1戰勝[[摩洛哥國家足球隊|摩洛哥國家足球隊]]。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.goal.com/en-za/news/4622/africa/2013/08/15/4188120/african-friendly-round-up-report-burkina-faso-stun-morocco |title=African friendly round-up report: Burkina Faso stun Morocco, as Egypt, Tunisia knock off opponents |publisher=Goal.com |date=15 August 2013 |accessdate=11 January 2014 |archive-date=2019-07-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190720095936/https://www.goal.com/en-za/news/4622/africa/2013/08/15/4188120/african-friendly-round-up-report-burkina-faso-stun-morocco |dead-url=no }}</ref> 
在[[2015年非洲國家盃|2015年非洲國家盃]]，分組賽3場賽堩有出場，並在首2仗得到正選。

